data.description:
Introducing a charming 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath residence boasting a blend of modern upgrades and timeless elegance. This meticulously maintained home showcases a brand-new roof, ensuring peace of mind for years to come. Updated windows flood the interior with natural light, accentuating the spacious layout and enhancing energy efficiency with the lower level wooding-burning fireplace and a walk-out sliding door to the backyard. The kitchen boasts sleek, contemporary appliances, perfect for culinary enthusiasts.

Nestled within the expansive backyard is a generously sized storage shed, providing ample space for all your outdoor essentials. With its four well-appointed bedrooms, this home offers versatility and comfort. Ideal for growing families or those seeking extra space for guests... or home offices. Don't miss the opportunity to experience the convenience and comfort this property has to offer.
